.DT
pub shop
Discworld room help
pub shop

.SH Name
.SI 5
pub shop - a place that sells food and drink to the masses
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
list
buy <drink|food> [for <person>]
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a room help file.

A nice place that gives a choice of alcoholic or other sorts of beverages
to buy.  A pub can sell either food or drink or both, and can also allow you
to buy things for other people.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> buy orange juice
> buy rat and ketchup for dwarf
> buy beer for vimes,nobby,colon,angua
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
pub
.EP
